divs: Sighting DetailsI seen a strange looking cloud while I was at work floating over the park across the street so I took a picture of it. To the naked eye you couldn't see the dark circle inside of it. I was at work at the time. I took the picture because I like taking pictures of clouds and this was an unusual shape and low. I'd say about 50 to 100 feet above the park and it just floated there. I went back to work and it was gone when I looked back. So when I went home I downloaded the picture in my computer, it came out with a dark circle on the inside of it. Have no clue what it is, why it is like it is. Maybe it's a vortex, wormhole or something.
